Description: # snapshottest_ext
        
        extra formatter for snapshottest
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```python
        # use with pytest
        import pandas as pd
        from dataframe import PandasSnapshot
        def test_format(snapshot):
            df = pd.DataFrame([['a', 'b'], ['c', 'd']],
                              columns=['col 1', 'col 2'])
            snapshot.assert_match(PandasSnapshot(df))
        ```
        
